data.description: Nestled in Franklin Lakes on a quiet cul-de-sac, this two-story, four-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom home is a sanctuary of comfort. The generous backyard offers serene pond views, while a covered front porch welcomes you inside. High end kitchen applinces. WashTower Stacked SMART Laundry Center. An open eat-in kitchen and family room make hosting a breeze, and a spacious back patio invites you to relax amidst nature. Conveniently located just minutes from the dog park, public pool, and Franklin bike trails, this home promises a well-rounded lifestyle. With its charm, space, and prime location, it's a must-see for those seeking a harmonious blend of tranquility and convenience in Franklin Lakes.
